SUMMARY:Construction Simulator | Ep. 35 - Finishing the Car Park Before
 Anyone Notices My Mistakes
DESCRIPTION:Back on the construction site for another evening of heavy
 machinery, big projects, and whatever fresh challenges the game decides to
 throw at me this time. Construction Simulator is back - bigger and better
 than ever! Take charge of over 70 machines, dozens of them brand new to
 the franchise, and build to your heart's content on two huge maps - on
 your own or with your friends!
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=siugcYqVG4g
CATEGORIES:Construction Simulator
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
