LAST-MODIFIED:20260621T234000Z
DTSTART:20260617T203000Z
DTEND:20260617T223000Z
SUMMARY:Sniper Elite III | Ep. 4 - Fort Rifugio
DESCRIPTION:The desert campaign continues with stealth, precision, and
 carefully planned shots. Hopefully carefully planned, anyway. Sniper Elite
 3 is a tactical third-person shooter that combines stealth, gameplay
 choice and genre-defining ballistics with huge, open levels and the exotic
 terrain of World War 2 North Africa.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NqHMdB2V_s4
CATEGORIES:Sniper Elite III
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
