UID:stream-23652211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260529T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260621T234000Z
DTSTART:20260619T203000Z
DTEND:20260619T223000Z
SUMMARY:Dune: Awakening | Ep. 25 - Arrakis Update: Still Full of Sand
DESCRIPTION:The journey through the frontier continues. Tough choices,
 unforgettable moments, and a world that never stops testing you. Rise from
 survival to greatness and challenge the power of an Imperium in Dune:
 Awakening, a brand-new open world survival and crafting game. Alone or
 together with others, you must survive the sandworm, build a home, craft
 your ornithopter, and unravel the story of the missing Fremen.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6N2VLTD6pHk
CATEGORIES:Dune: Awakening
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-23662211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260530T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260621T234000Z
DTSTART:20260620T203000Z
DTEND:20260620T223000Z
SUMMARY:Fallout 4 | Ep. 51 - Final Mission of Nuka-World. I Hope They Have
 Souvenirs
DESCRIPTION:It's finally time for the last mission in Nuka-World! Will we
 survive? Will we regret everything? Will there be souvenirs? Tune in and
 find out. As the sole survivor of Vault 111, you enter a world destroyed
 by nuclear war. Every second is a fight for survival, and every choice is
 yours. Only you can rebuild and determine the fate of the Wasteland.
 Welcome home.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6VS1RYe1G9s
CATEGORIES:Fallout 4
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
