SUMMARY:Construction Simulator | Ep. 36 - The Building Looks Straight From
 This Angle
DESCRIPTION:Back on the construction site! Everything is going according
 to plan... provided you stand in exactly the right spot and don't ask too
 many questions. Construction Simulator is back - bigger and better than
 ever! Take charge of over 70 machines, dozens of them brand new to the
 franchise, and build to your heart's content on two huge maps - on your
 own or with your friends!
