SUMMARY:Dune: Awakening | Ep. 26 - The Landsraad Has Asked Me for Favors.
 Mistake
DESCRIPTION:Politics on Arrakis? What could possibly go wrong? The answer
 is probably everything. Join me as we navigate alliances, survival, and
 endless sand. Rise from survival to greatness and challenge the power of
 an Imperium in Dune: Awakening, a brand-new open world survival and
 crafting game. Alone or together with others, you must survive the
 sandworm, build a home, craft your ornithopter, and unravel the story of
 the missing Fremen.
URL:https://www.twitch.tv/dr_ravenholm
CATEGORIES:Dune: Awakening
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
