SUMMARY:Sniper Elite III | Ep. 5 - Siwa Oasis
DESCRIPTION:The desert campaign continues with stealth, precision, and
 tactical gameplay. Every shot counts, and every mistake is... usually
 quite loud. Sniper Elite 3 is a tactical third-person shooter that
 combines stealth, gameplay choice and genre-defining ballistics with huge,
 open levels and the exotic terrain of World War 2 North Africa.
URL:https://www.twitch.tv/dr_ravenholm
